description:
Service Usage

This services provides the ability to match parties using Biometric data (facial, finger, retna) with filters such as the biographic data in a real time service.
readme:
Service Usage

This services provides the ability to match parties using Biometric data (facial, finger, retna) with filters such as the biographic data in a real time service.
This service expects to be able to match the party to a single known entity but can also return multiple matches. Limits exist for the number of parties to be returned and checks that the party does not appear on a watch list.
You can supply many biometric images within the request. The service is expected to be a real time service only. This service does not register the biomtric image.
